Naruto the Movie 2 English Dubbed

Naruto the Movie 2 - Legend of the Stone of Gelel

Outline:
Naruto, Shikamaru, and Sakura are on a mission to deliver a lost pet to a certain village. However, right in the middle of everything, troops led by the mysterious knight, Temujin, attack them. When the three become separated, Naruto and Temujin fight, only to end up falling off a cliff. When Shikamaru discovers a strange moving fortress, he decides to investigate on his own. Just what lies inside the mysterious fortress? What happened to Naruto and Temujin? And how is the Hidden Sand Village involved in all of this?
